text: Market News March 2, 2018 / 2:14 PM / in 24 minutes BRIEF-Jaguar Health Says Unit Napo Pharmaceuticals Signs Deal With Transition Patient Services To Establish Nationwide Pilot "Mytesi Direct" Program Reuters Staff 1 Min Read March 2 (Reuters) - Jaguar Health Inc: * JAGUAR HEALTH - UNIT NAPO PHARMACEUTICALS SIGNS DEAL WITH TRANSITION PATIENT SERVICES TO ESTABLISH NATIONWIDE PILOT“MYTESI DIRECT” PROGRAM * JAGUAR HEALTH - UNDER DEAL TERMS, TRANSITION PATIENT SERVICES WILL OPERATE NATIONWIDE PILOT PROGRAM FOR MYTESI, EXPECTED TO BEGIN THIS MARCH Source text: ( bit.ly/2F6983y ) Further company coverage:
